    • allowedBatchSizes

      public BatchFunction.Options allowedBatchSizes(List<Long> allowedBatchSizes)
      Sets the allowedBatchSizes option.
      Parameters:
      allowedBatchSizes - Optional list of allowed batch sizes. If left empty, does nothing. Otherwise, supplies a list of batch sizes, causing the op to pad batches up to one of those sizes. The entries must increase monotonically. If enable_large_batch_splitting is false (i.e., large-input-split is not enabled) the final entry must equal max_batch_size.
      Returns:
      this Options instance.

    • allowedBatchSizes

      public BatchFunction.Options allowedBatchSizes(Long... allowedBatchSizes)
      Sets the allowedBatchSizes option.
      Parameters:
      allowedBatchSizes - Optional list of allowed batch sizes. If left empty, does nothing. Otherwise, supplies a list of batch sizes, causing the op to pad batches up to one of those sizes. The entries must increase monotonically. If enable_large_batch_splitting is false (i.e., large-input-split is not enabled) the final entry must equal max_batch_size.
      Returns:
      this Options instance.

    • sharedName

      public BatchFunction.Options sharedName(String sharedName)
      Sets the sharedName option.
      Parameters:
      sharedName - Concurrently running instances of batch in the same device with the same container and shared_name will batch their elements together. If left empty, the op name will be used as the shared name.
      Returns:
      this Options instance.
